@startuml seq-11-upload
' 序列图11：上传图片
title 上传图片序列图

actor 用户 as User
participant "前端" as Front
participant "UploadController" as Ctrl
participant "ImageUtil" as ImgUtil
participant "UploadUtil" as UpUtil
participant "本地磁盘" as Disk

User -> Front: wx.chooseImage选择图片
Front -> Ctrl: wx.uploadFile POST /api/upload
Ctrl -> ImgUtil: isImage(filename)校验扩展名
ImgUtil --> Ctrl: true
Ctrl -> UpUtil: saveFile(file)
UpUtil -> UpUtil: 生成UUID文件名
UpUtil -> UpUtil: 按日期分目录(yyyy-MM-dd)
UpUtil -> Disk: 写入uploads/yyyy-MM-dd/xxx.jpg
Disk --> UpUtil: 成功
UpUtil --> Ctrl: /uploads/yyyy-MM-dd/xxx.jpg
Ctrl --> Front: {url: /uploads/.../xxx.jpg}
Front -> Front: _fixUrl()拼接baseUrl
Front --> User: 预览图片

@enduml
